ht-year\">2025</span> Traffic Cop Labs. All rights reserved.\r\n          </p>\r\n\r\n        </div>\r\n      </footer>\r\n    `;\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\ncustomElements.define('tcl-footer', TCLFooter);\r\n</script>",
